structure.unit: PHYSICIANS, OSTEOPATHS, PODIATRISTS, AND RELATED MEDICAL PRACTITIONERS

law.history: Repealed 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 36, effective July 15, 2002; amended 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 21, effective July 15, 2002. -- Created 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 190, sec. 16, effective July 15, 1994.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/2002). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 36, prevails over its amendment in 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 21.
